        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Kaufe sie, wenn:</strong> You're a professional videographer, documentary filmmaker, or commercial shooter who needs compact cinema quality with exceptional low-light. You value professional audio and unlimited recording times.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Ãœberspringe sie, wenn:</strong> You need hybrid photo/video (get A7S III), want higher resolution (get FX6), or are budget-conscious (ZV-E1 offers similar sensor for $1,700 less).
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

